Returns a valid table id to check in or make reservation (based on the restaurant's policy):
For 1 or 2 pax: Only allocates tables of 2 or 4 pax. For 3 or 4 pax: Only allocates tables of 4 or 6 pax. For 5 or 6 pax: Only allocates tables of 6 or 8 pax. For 9 or 10 pax: Only allocates tables of 10 pax.
